<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa ka neih zakcha puong ka,
 Amah chuh panpih ka;
 Amah thu chuh zah bawl zing ka,
 A Kross lopina tawh.

[V2]
 Kross achun, Kross achun vak ka muh patna ah,
 Ka lunggil gikpuok chu a kilik mang;
 Ziechun gin ziekin mitvakna ka mu'i,
 Tun chuh nicheng in ka kipak tai.

[V3]
 2. Pathien, Isu Amin ka he'i,
 Amin chuh ka taksang;
 Ka thagau suzahhuoi puonna,
 Ka kinep thawn puona.

[V4]
 3. Lalchutphah banga thutiem det,
 Hun guot atun chanin;
 Amah khuta ka vawpsak chuh,
 Phatak in A vawp thei.

[V5]
 4. Ka min mantak lo chuh pu'n tin,
 A Pa masang achun;
 Van Jerusalem thak achun,
 Ka Thagau mun piena.</lyrics>
<title>AT THE CROSS</title>
<hymn_number>109</hymn_number>
</song>